# Worker and Scheduling — Thiên Nam Engine

> Rules for BullMQ workers: background job processing, scheduling, and idempotency.

---

## Core Principle: Jobs Must Be Idempotent

A job can be safely retried. If a job fails mid-execution, running it again should produce the same result without side effects.

---

## Job Types

### Scheduled Jobs (BullMQ Recurring)

| Job Name | Schedule | Purpose |
|----------|----------|---------|
| `daily-reset` | Daily at 00:00 UTC | Daily rewards, cooldown resets, heartbeat |
| `heart-demon-decay` | Daily at 00:00 UTC | -1 heart demon per active character |
| `injury-expiry` | Every 5 minutes | Check and clear expired injuries |
| `cooldown-expiry` | Every 5 minutes | Check and clear expired cooldowns |
| `season-check` | Every hour | Check season end conditions |
| `sect-salary` | Weekly (Sunday 00:00 UTC) | Distribute sect salaries |
| `world-event-expiry` | Every 15 minutes | End expired world events |
| `leaderboard-refresh` | Every hour | Recalculate all leaderboards |

### Delayed Jobs (One-time, BullMQ Delayed)

| Job Name | Trigger | Purpose |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `seclusion-complete` | `/cultivate` with SECLUSION mode | Apply seclusion rewards after 8 hours |
| `alchemy-complete` | `/alchemy` | Apply alchemy result |
| `encounter-timeout` | `/encounter` | Clear stuck encounter state |
| `mission-expiry` | `/mission` | Handle expired missions |
| `world-boss-spawn` | Admin spawn command | Schedule boss spawn |
| `world-boss-despawn` | Boss spawn or admin command | Remove boss after duration |
| `season-reward` | Season end | Distribute season rewards |

### Event-Driven Jobs (BullMQ Queue)

| Job Name | Trigger | Purpose |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `process-public-log` | Any action with `publicLog: true` | Send Discord public log message |
| `process-admin-action` | Admin panel mutation | Send admin action log |
| `send-player-notification` | Various triggers | DM player about important events |

