## Scheduling with Cron

### Daily Reset (00:00 UTC)

```typescript
import { CronRepeatOption } from "bullmq";

dailyQueue.add(
  "daily-reset",
  { resetType: "daily" },
  {
    repeat: {
      pattern: "0 0 * * *", // Every day at midnight UTC
      tz: "UTC",
    } as CronRepeatOption,
  }
);
```

### Weekly Sect Salary (Sunday 00:00 UTC)

```typescript
sectSalaryQueue.add(
  "sect-salary",
  { salaryType: "weekly" },
  {
    repeat: {
      pattern: "0 0 * * 0", // Every Sunday at midnight UTC
      tz: "UTC",
    } as CronRepeatOption,
  }
);
```

