## Monitoring

### Metrics to Track

| Metric | Alert Threshold |
|--------|----------------|
| Queue depth | > 1000 jobs pending |
| Job failure rate | > 5% in 1 hour |
| Avg job duration | > 30 seconds |
| Redis memory | > 80% of max |
| Worker process count | 0 (crash!) |

### Health Checks

```typescript
// Worker health check endpoint
app.get("/worker/health", async (req, res) => {
  const workerCounts = await dailyQueue.getJobCounts();
  const isHealthy = workerCounts.active + workerCounts.waiting < 1000;

  res.json({
    status: isHealthy ? "healthy" : "degraded",
    queueDepth: workerCounts.waiting,
    activeJobs: workerCounts.active,
    failedJobs: workerCounts.failed,
    timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
  });
});
```

