## Adding a New Job

1. Define job data interface in `apps/worker/src/jobs/types.ts`
2. Add to queue definition in `apps/worker/src/queues/`
3. Implement handler with idempotency checks
4. Add retry configuration
5. Write unit tests
6. Document in `kb/engineering/worker-jobs.md`
